        "content": [
          "Catch. Carry. Change. Uncle. Cousin.",
          "Flower. River. City. Honour. Peace.",
          "",
          "These feel like the most English words",
          "in English. They aren't. Every one of",
          "them arrived with the Normans in 1066",
          "and quietly refused to leave.",
          "",
          "If French, Spanish, Italian or",
          "Portuguese is your first language,",
          "half of Tier 1 already belongs to you.",
          "The words will feel like coming home.",
          "",
          "But the real lesson lives in the Notes.",
          "That's where the Germanic half of",
          "English waits — the older, plainer",
          "words that native speakers reach for",
          "without thinking."
